a required","label":"b Data required","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1132–7/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1132–7","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs1132%E2%80%937%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall require an institution of higher education referred to in subsection (a) to report information listed in subsection (a) to the Secretary consistent with the requirements of .section 1011f of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
